<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日，<delay20 />
你也是来庆生的吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你还真是重情义啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也会尽自己的一份力，<delay20 />
给寿星过一个最棒的生日！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好了，<delay20 />你也要<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打起精神来！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天过生日的主角<delay8 />是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们作为朋友，<delay8 />
要尽力为寿星好好庆祝才是！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />高兴，<delay20 />
我也就会不自觉地笑起来呢！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的笑容！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是很难得能看到这家伙<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么生气勃勃的样子呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能办出最棒的生日会，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我们<delay8 />
可要嗨起来啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay20 />我们是第一次见吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我叫<tag a="110" b="10" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能在这里遇到，也是一种缘分吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日，<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是朋友出生的特别日子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想着要为寿星热闹地庆祝一下！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在，我还认识了你，<delay20 />
今天也成为了我特别的日子呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后也请多关照啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为朋友庆祝生日，<delay20 />
是一件很开心的事呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年也好，<delay8 />后年也好，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都会尽我所能为他们庆祝的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生日派对上，<delay20 />你玩得开心吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />看上去很开心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉自己用心的准备都值得了！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是我的生日派对<delay20 />
也能这么热闹就好了。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为什么<delay20 />只要看到<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生日蛋糕摆在那里，<delay20 />
就会开始兴奋起来呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我以前一直梦想，<delay20 />
要一个人吃下一整个大蛋糕！<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，最近完全没有这样的想法了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起一个人吃独食，<delay20 />
和朋友分享<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉更加美味呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来我也变成熟了呢！</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">生日派对的装饰品，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉很不错，不是吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天<delay20 />和大家一起努力装饰的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />装饰好的房间比平时华丽得多。<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很有过生日的特别感，很不错吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能像这样，<delay20 />为朋友新的一年的开始<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送上祝福，<delay20 />我很高兴。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />好像<delay20 />
也很享受今天的派对呢！<delay20 />
太好了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你把生日礼物<delay20 />
给<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天，<delay20 />我和那家伙闲聊的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看着好像很期待<delay20 />
你的礼物呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种东西，<delay20 />最重要的是心意！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要是你用心挑选的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对方一定会很高兴的！</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我从以前开始，<delay20 />
就不太擅长<delay8 />挑礼物呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到最后，还是没送出手的情况也有过。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种东西重要的不是礼物本身，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最重要的是“送礼物”这件事。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay20 />你也要鼓起勇气，<delay20 />把礼物送出去。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />那家伙呀，<delay20 />
只要是你送的礼物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是什么，一定都会很高兴的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />给<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日礼物，<delay20 />
你想好送什么了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我挑选了最保险的日用品，<delay20 />
是不是应该<delay8 />更有冒险精神比较好？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年，<delay20 />我会争取挑些特别的东西。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />这不是<tag a="110" b="3" />吗！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也<delay8 />搬来这座岛了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后请多关照啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我会去
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的<delay8 />生日派对，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也一起<delay8 />来玩吧！</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀！<delay20 />这不是<tag a="110" b="3" />吗！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在<delay8 />就住在这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到会在这里遇见你。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在大家正在一起庆祝呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以的话，<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也来加入我们吧！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />我之前没见过你呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我叫<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="10" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你能记住我！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天来这里参加
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的<delay8 />生日派对！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要一起来庆祝？</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天好忙啊～！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的生日和情人节，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />活动真是多啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也送你这个！</message>
	<message label="020_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是啊～</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然对我来说朋友的生日比较重要，<delay40 />
