<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天不管走到哪里，<delay8 />都很热闹呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以的话，请收下这个</message>
	<message label="021_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能是的呢</message>
